 CLOSED TREE\n\nSummary: dustin's updating the documentation in https://github.com/taskcluster/taskcluster-notify/pull/33/files\n\nReviewers: jlorenzo\n\nReviewed By: jlorenzo\n\nBug #: 1459185\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D1132", "files": ["taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/release_notifications.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4338d94776b0087684aa091a8293334fe3140500", "parents": ["e6f9ade8bca744a9abaef3efd18e9653ff2c029a"], "tags": []}], "date": 1525444120, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "sfraser@mozilla.com"}, "9182": {"changesets": [{"author": "Hiroyuki Ikezoe \u003chikezoe@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1457107 - Don't throttle visibility change animations if the animation element isn't on out-of-view element. r=birtles\n\nIn bug 1237454, we introduced a new change hint that is produced when\nvisibility property is changed from 'visible' to 'hidden' or from 'hidden'\nto 'visible'.  Animations producing this new change hint can be throttled\nif the animation element is out-of-view, but can not be throttled in the case\nwhere the element is in-view. In the bug, a test case for a visibility change\nanimation on out-of-view element was added, but no test for in-view case was\nadded.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: BhiRm13rfRr", "files": ["dom/animation/KeyframeEffectReadOnly.cpp", "dom/animation/KeyframeEffectReadOnly.h", "dom/animation/test/mozilla/file_restyles.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5bd14318ff8e16c993e15d59812469e21161042a", "parents": ["5bf13799a1fcb612701222f8f877afc45eb7254f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Henrik Skupin \u003cmail@hskupin.info\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1396185 - [wdspec] Remove unwanted docstring references to the spec. r=ato\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: AMWiBBFO1jP", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/webdriver/tests/navigation/get_title.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8d074598b6caa5c59453e933da5d64e72e10a842", "parents": ["5bd14318ff8e16c993e15d59812469e21161042a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Henrik Skupin \u003cmail@hskupin.info\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1396185 - [wdspec] Use shared get_title function for making HTTP requests. r=ato\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 8gYWouT6K8q", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/webdriver/tests/navigation/get_title.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9c47feeac73f3fe2da0e80903a5fdf157d781ada", "parents": ["8d074598b6caa5c59453e933da5d64e72e10a842"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Henrik Skupin \u003cmail@hskupin.info\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1396185 - [wdspec] Fix linter failures in get_title.py. r=ato\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: KxrB69Bakcv", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/webdriver/tests/navigation/get_title.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7c1c51eea5338c5b3332cc368c119300aefed7f2", "parents": ["9c47feeac73f3fe2da0e80903a5fdf157d781ada"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Henrik Skupin \u003cmail@hskupin.info\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1396185 - [wdspec] Fix race condition in test_title_after_modification. r=ato\n\nUsing \"WebDriver:ExecuteScript\" to set the document title can cause\na race condition when the title gets retrieved from the parent process.\nTo guard against it \"wait()\" should be used.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: DyrHpQSKLjy", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/webdriver/tests/navigation/get_title.py.ini", "testing/web-platform/tests/webdriver/tests/navigation/get_title.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "dc74ac930ef1523fa34ad0c428efb92b0e08b3f4", "parents": ["7c1c51eea5338c5b3332cc368c119300aefed7f2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "AlvaroRe \u003carb952@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1440577 - Marionette has to use \"eForceQuit\" for in_app shutdown and restart requests r=whimboo\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: KEwEg7AK7yu", "files": ["testing/marionette/client/marionette_driver/marionette.py"], "git_node"