the transform\noperation list.\n\nI cannot make any sense of what the old code was trying to do.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 5BtCiueEPlR\n", "files": ["servo/components/style/properties/helpers/animated_properties.mako.rs", "servo/components/style/values/computed/transform.rs"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5d477ed8d62de3ff678519f79fc3ac9f23bb91cc", "parents": ["2d910b41bff477568a84ab3c65656cb744b2ae84"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Haik Aftandilian \u003chaftandilian@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1458553 - Return of Google Maps all black map with updated Nvidia web driver on Mac r=Alex_Gaynor\n\nUpdate Mac sandbox rules to allow executable mappings from /Library/GPUBundles which is\nused by the Nvidia downloadable \"Web\" driver.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: L2nTP4YWdJJ", "files": ["security/sandbox/mac/SandboxPolicies.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d67ad5505bc5ebb2e0f4ecc0864b6021adc2473f", "parents": ["5d477ed8d62de3ff678519f79fc3ac9f23bb91cc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1458715: followup: don't fix distance computation so fast. r=me\n\nOn a CLOSED TREE\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 1Y3As81hnRx\n", "files": ["servo/components/style/properties/helpers/animated_properties.mako.rs"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "62a80b3ee6fa31f1fea3371d5d82515a6cf8dc4a", "parents": ["d67ad5505bc5ebb2e0f4ecc0864b6021adc2473f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Marco Bonardo \u003cmbonardo@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1354531 - Remove PlacesUtils.asyncHistory to make History internals access less convenient. r=standard8\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: K9oQTJbVAZF", "files": ["browser/components/extensions/test/xpcshell/test_ext_history.js", "services/sync/modules/engines/history.js", "services/sync/tests/unit/test_history_engine.js", "toolkit/components/downloads/test/unit/test_DownloadList.js", "toolkit/components/p