 Luong \u003cgabriel.luong@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1458751 - Lazy load StyleInspectorMenu, KeyShortscut and clipboardHelper in CssRuleView and CssComputedView. r=pbro", "files": ["devtools/client/inspector/computed/computed.js", "devtools/client/inspector/rules/rules.js", "devtools/client/inspector/shared/test/browser_styleinspector_context-menu-copy-color_01.js", "devtools/client/inspector/test/shared-head.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8f9fc394b2c407b1fe5ac352bbd7c97c511ac117", "parents": ["8cfe37c47c9bf36408adc3e6de1b131efe227832"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan de Mooij \u003cjdemooij@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1458567 part 1 - Don't invoke interrupt callback and Debugger onStep hook for internal JS engine interrupts. r=luke", "files": ["js/public/Utility.h", "js/src/gc/Allocator.cpp", "js/src/gc/GC.cpp", "js/src/irregexp/NativeRegExpMacroAssembler.cpp", "js/src/jit/BaselineCompiler.cpp", "js/src/jit/CodeGenerator.cpp", "js/src/jit/CompileWrappers.cpp", "js/src/jit/CompileWrappers.h", "js/src/jsapi.cpp", "js/src/vm/HelperThreads.cpp", "js/src/vm/JSContext-inl.h", "js/src/vm/JSContext.cpp", "js/src/vm/JSContext.h", "js/src/vm/Runtime.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "693e9f7a2b5983c71e0e2de324335cc7ef990611", "parents": ["8f9fc394b2c407b1fe5ac352bbd7c97c511ac117"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan de Mooij \u003cjdemooij@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1458567 part 2 - Remove now unnecessary dom.max_chrome_script_run_time entry from browser_preferences_usage.js test. r=johannh", "files": ["browser/base/content/test/performance/browser_preferences_usage.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1eb83ac9acee5653c4a8eb80e847a7b8391d8f41", "parents": ["693e9f7a2b5983c71e0e2de324335cc7ef990611"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Eugen Sawin \u003cesawin@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1458687 - [1.0] Remove obsolete isUserTriggered argument in nsContentUtils::TriggerLink. r=smaug\n", "files": ["dom/base/Element.cpp", "dom/base/nsContentUtils.cpp", "dom/base/nsContentUtils.h", "layout/generic/nsImageFrame.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6580f1d8857df294a99c12f40ecb9b8e4e807354", "parents": ["1eb83ac9acee5653c4a8eb80e847a7b8391d8f41"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ryan Hunt \u003crhunt@eqrion.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1458462 - Create paint workers if it's possible we could switch to tiling in the future. r=nical\n\nOn windows it's possible for us to fallback from D2D to Skia rendering at any time due to a device reset.\nIf this happens with `enable-tiles-if-skia-pomtp` enabled we could begin to use tiling. This can cause a\ncrash if we never created the worker threads because at initialization time we weren't using tiling.\n\nAnother way to fix this would be to dynamically create the worker threads in UpdateRenderMode if we\nhave switched to skia. That's a larger change and more might be required, so I'd rather just fix the\ncrash for now.\n\nThis commit also fixes a pref that should be `Once` instead of `Live`.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: JQidXPjI7ER", "files": ["gfx/layers/PaintThread.cpp", "gfx/thebes/gfxPrefs.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "895146c6b6bcb5a1fa447cdcb54f1925a5ce862a", "parents": ["6580f1d8857df294a99c12f40ecb9b8e4e807354"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan de Mooij \u003cjdemooij@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1458198 - Assert the frontend reported an exception if it fails to compile a script. r=jorendorff", "files": ["js/src/frontend/BytecodeCompiler.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ce42829bf9486a4f756de98a07495bce8852b836", "parents": ["895146c6b6bcb5a1fa447cdcb54f1925a5ce862a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan de Mooij \u003cjdemooij@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1458456 part 1 - Don't call JSFunction::needsSomeEnvironmentObject off-thread. r=jonco", "files": ["js/src/jit/CodeGenerator.cpp", "js/src/jit/CompileInfo.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a73309432c550506126afeb668831f83709ed54a", "parents": ["ce42829bf9486a4f756de98a07495bce8852b836"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan de Mooij \u003cjdemooij@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1458456 part 2 - Move NEW_SCRIPT_CLEARED flag from BaseShape to JSFunction. r=tcampbell", "files": ["js/src/vm/JSFunction.h", "js/src/vm/JSObject.cpp", "js/src/vm/NativeObject.h", "js/src/vm/Shape.h", "js/src/vm/TypeInference.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "12c2522509f87e093b6385fa5d99dcc10aee2776", "parents": ["a73309432c550506126afeb668831f83709ed54a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Dorel Luca \u003cdluca@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out 4 changesets (bug 1458791, bug 1458769, bug 1458751, bug 1458758) for Mochitest failure on multiple files. CLOSED TREE\n\nBacked out changeset 8f9fc394b2c4 (bug 1458751)\nBacked out changeset 8cfe37c47c9b (bug 1458758)\nBacked out changeset dd0fa5821bd1 (bug 1458769)\nBacked out changeset d09be370108d (bug 1458791)", "files": ["devtools/client/inspector/boxmodel/box-model.js", "devtools/client/inspector/boxmodel/utils/editing-session.js", "devtools/client/inspector/computed/computed.js", "devtools/client/inspector/inspector.js", "devtools/client/inspector/rules/rules.js", "devtools/client/inspector/shared/style-inspector-menu.js", "devtools/client/inspector/shared/test/browser_styleinspector_context-menu-copy-color_01.js", "devtools/client/inspector/test/shared-head.js", "devtools/client/inspector/toolsidebar.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3bcc98e23806594f2f9bccdd2596c37a5db7187d", "parents": ["12c2522509f87e093b6385fa5d99dcc10aee2776"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andrea Marchesini \u003camarchesini@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1458836 - No needs to inform WorkerHolders when in Closing state, r=bkelly", "