nch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 4268240fb6d9b8a56058477017a345f87cae799f with FENNEC_61_0b7_BUILD1, FENNEC_61_0b7_RELEASE a=release CLOSED TREE", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "910bd400d7128e99b9bd0949c49a7a5d7651e57a", "parents": ["7219511f506b7a2200f74c6579bb0b4e35870ac8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "\"Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e\"", "branch": "default", "desc": "Automatic version bump CLOSED TREE NO BUG a=release", "files": ["browser/config/version_display.txt"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "73c9465372bc35418c8348cf079b473addeeda59", "parents": ["910bd400d7128e99b9bd0949c49a7a5d7651e57a"], "tags": []}], "date": 1527002507, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "9247": {"changesets": [{"author": "\"Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e\"", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 4268240fb6d9b8a56058477017a345f87cae799f with FIREFOX_61_0b7_BUILD1, FIREFOX_61_0b7_RELEASE a=release CLOSED TREE", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b4608745ceec3d5274c7392f3e60300ba02ad42b", "parents": ["73c9465372bc35418c8348cf079b473addeeda59"], "tags": []}], "date": 1527004872, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "9248": {"changesets": [{"author": "\"Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e\"", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 4268240fb6d9b8a56058477017a345f87cae799f with DEVEDITION_61_0b7_BUILD1, DEVEDITION_61_0b7_RELEASE a=release CLOSED TREE", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8284f435a1cb5681c3dd2d08591aa5df2d8d5846", "parents": ["b4608745ceec3d5274c7392f3e60300ba02ad42b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1527005053, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "9249": {"changesets": [{"author": "Julien Cristau \u003cjcristau@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Post beta 7: unset EARLY_BETA_OR_EARLIER. a=release", "files": ["build/defines.sh"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3debc4b081a3201cbc7b51d7fef1650b7032e384", "parents": ["8284f435a1cb5681c3dd2d08591aa5df2d8d5846"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Julien Cristau \u003cjcristau@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug: Turn off staged rollout for Fennec. a=release", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/push-apk/kind.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f8c381b7d9a42ecbe4ed34792cd98430b32b6dd0", "parents": ["3debc4b081a3201cbc7b51d7fef1650b7032e384"], "tags": []}], "date": 1527009729, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "9250": {"changesets": [{"author": "Nick Thomas \u003cnthomas@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1463622 - errors running the partner repack script should be fatal, r=Callek, a=release\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: BgTyPWfXVFj", "files": ["testing/mozharness/scripts/desktop_partner_repacks.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a4753784833d68799720789ce80526eed1d0e084", "parents": ["f8c381b7d9a42ecbe4ed34792cd98430b32b6dd0"], "tags": []}], "date": 1527042763, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "nthomas@mozilla.com"}, "9251": {"changesets": [{"author": "Ryan Hunt \u003crhunt@eqrion.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1420865 - Don't check for CONTENT_MAY_CHANGE_TRANSFORM across layer trees. r=mstange, a=RyanVM\n\nMayResample() is used on the content and compositor to determine whether the whole\nvisible region should be or should have been validated. This calculation is done\npartially by traversing ancestor layers and looking for a flag. This can return\ndifferent values then in the content side versus the shadow side, which in this\ncase leads to artifacts.\n\nThis commit tries to solve the problem by ignoring layers that content is unaware\nof. This works, but has the downside that resampling artifacts could show up if\nthe parent process is truly doing animations that require resampling.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 4TW6nzxS6E", "files": ["gfx/layers/Layers.cpp", "gfx/layers/Layers.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "151ea913c9a32f499bbfb077e331554c0d251e83", "parents": ["a4753784833d68799720789ce80526eed1d0e084"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Yura Zenevich \u003cyura.zenevich@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1441187 - Wait for non-stale state instead of non-busy when waiting for root document accessible. r=pbro, a=RyanVM\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 4bEkg0us2xF", "files": ["devtools/server/actors/accessibility.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5e73575edddf28dbf6eb5a8d3d4cb079e38472da", "parents": ["151ea913c9a32f499bbfb077e331554c0d251e83"], "tags": []}, {"author": "sotaro \u003csotaro.ikeda.g@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1437334 - Block DX NV12 on SandyBridge for old graphics drivers. r=jrmuizel, a=RyanVM", "files": ["gfx/config/gfxVars.h", "gfx/thebes/D3D11Checks.cpp", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatform.cpp", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatform.h", "widget/GfxInfoBase.cpp", "widget/nsIGfxInfo.idl", "widget/windows/GfxInfo.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7195b1005f8cc917ca3183bedb956a05df1c3844", "parents": ["5e73575edddf28dbf6eb5a8d3d4cb079e38472da"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Peter Van der Beken \u003cpeterv@propagandism.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1457301 - Crash in mozilla::ipc::ProcessLink::SendMessage | IPC_Message_Name=PBrowser::Msg_AsyncMessage. r=mccr8, a=RyanVM\n\nAdd back code to block big messages in DispatchAsyncMessage that wasn't added to the\ncodepath used by the WebIDL bindings. Also remove the non-WebIDL version of\nDispatchAsyncMessage, as it's now unused.", "files": ["dom/base/nsFrameMessageManager.cpp", "dom/base/nsFrameMessageManager.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "175d58ad6bd1acec5554c97ac14ae23f18c60c9a", "parents": ["7195b1005f8cc917ca3183bedb956a05df1c3844"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jeff Gilbert \u003cjgilbert@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1461293 - TexStorage needs only one of w,h,d\u003e\u003e(levels-1) to be non-zero. r=kvark, a=RyanVM\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: IUlrfWrLdUc", "files": ["dom/canvas/WebGLTextureUpload.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "818acd7faa4cff769ca7696b6a66b80e0ca9ff1c", "parents": ["175d58ad6bd1acec5554c97ac14ae23f18c60c9a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Bas Schouten \u003cbschouten@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1457758 - Blacklist NVidia driver 397.31. r=davidb, a=RyanVM\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 9IomfIWkmpb", "files": ["widget/windows/GfxInfo.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5429fc9810f3dafc6b12a9c0fb0b47c0e60ec33e", "parents": ["818acd7faa4cff769ca7696b6a66b80e0ca9ff1c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Michael Kaply \u003cmozilla@kaply.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1461805 - Don't show doorhanger for distribution add-ons. r=aswan, r=mstriemer, a=RyanVM\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: GjtVOWO8UFg", "files": ["browser/components/extensions/ExtensionControlledPopup.jsm", "browser/components/extensions/test/xpcshell/test_ext_distribution_popup.js", "browser/components/extensions/test/xpcshell/xpcshell-common.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9c23e9fb230f43afe6e9b95cedad2ff68cecd11e", "parents": ["5429fc9810f3dafc6b12a9c0fb0b47c0e60ec33e"], "tags": []}], "date": 1527083572, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "9252": {"changesets": [{"author": "William Lachance \u003cwlachance@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1461772 - Submit display version as a property of the fennec core ping. r=gsvelto, a=RyanVM\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: BFwgwOOo83s", "files": ["mobile/android/base/AppConstants.java.in", "mobile/android/base/generate_build_config.py", "mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/telemetry/pingbuilders/TelemetryCorePingBuilder.java", "toolkit/components/telemetry/docs/data/core-ping.rst"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b0a08f043830bf2caf21c757d2a19411e8d52667", "parents": ["9c23e9fb230f43afe6e9b95cedad2ff68cecd11e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jonathan Kew \u003cjkew@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1412882 - Rework gfxFontUtils::MapCharToGlyphFormat4 to be more robust. r=lsalzman, a=RyanVM", "files": ["gfx/thebes/gfxFontUtils.cpp", "gfx/thebes/gfxFontUtils.h", "gfx/thebes/gfxHarfBuzzShaper.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b403d2659f7792f66182890244c4da1320c4dfaa", "parents": ["b0a08f043830bf2caf21c757d2a19411e8d52667"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Steve Fink \u003csfink@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1456512 - Fixes for unwanted read barriers during minor GC: move JS::operator==(GCCellPtr,GCCellPtr) to the global scope to avoid shadowing, and add a dynamic check. r=jonco, a=RyanVM", "files": ["js/public/HeapAPI.h", "js/src/gc/Cell.h", "js/src/tests/non262/regress/regress-1456512-greyreadbarrier.js", "js/src/tests/non262/regress/regress-1456512.js", "js/src/tests/non262/regress/regress-1463421.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5dad30e8f67600619323c9e716e4218827b3073d", "parents": ["b403d2659f7792f66182890244c4da1320c4dfaa"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ben Kelly \u003cben@wanderview.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1461181 - Don't call ServiceWorkerManager::StartControllingClient() if there is no active worker. r=asuth, a=RyanVM", "files": ["dom/serviceworkers/ServiceWorkerManager.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b6f094b0dcf22966829312395b4a4c8dfb6aeb3d", "parents": ["5dad30e8f67600619323c9e716e4218827b3073d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Steve Fink \u003csfink@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1442722 - Move scope into JSStructuredData. r=baku, r=jorendorff, a=RyanVM", "files": ["dom/base/StructuredCloneBlob.cpp", "dom/base/nsFrameMessageManager.cpp", "dom/indexedDB/ActorsParent.cpp", "dom/indexedDB/IndexedDatabase.h", "dom/indexedDB/IndexedDatabaseInlines.h", "dom/ipc/StructuredCloneData.cpp", "dom/ipc/StructuredCloneData.h", "ipc/glue/IPCMessageUtils.h", "js/public/StructuredClone.h", "js/src/builtin/TestingFunctions.cpp", "js/src/fuzz-tests/testStructuredCloneReader.cpp", "js/src/vm/StructuredClone.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "eb37293b1520b2250847b73d969a1571da273d98", "parents": ["b6f094b0dcf22966829312395b4a4c8dfb6aeb3d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nicolas Chevobbe \u003cnchevobbe@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1463057 - Fix expanding object in console.error message. r=Honza, a=RyanVM\n\nThere was a race between the fetching of the object properties and the\nexpansion of the stacktrace of the console.error message. In the end, the\nmessage was re-rendered, without the object being expanded.\nTo prevent such thing, we stop the propagation of the click on the Tree\nnode. Here the fix is done directly in the Reps bundle so it can be applied\non beta, without unrelated code changes we'd have if doing a full bundle release.\nThe fix will be backported to the Tree components so it's included in the\nbundle on the next reps release.\nA test is added to make sure we don't regress this.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Di8YxJ7P1Wl", "files": ["devtools/client/shared/components/reps/reps.js", "devtools/client/webconsole/test/mochitest/browser.ini", "devtools/client/webconsole/test/mochitest/browser_webconsole_console_error_expand_object.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "29db38642cdd088356987980748adce41cc40130", "parents": ["eb37293b1520b2250847b73d969a1571da273d98"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Yura Zenevich \u003cyura.zenevich@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1461912 - Do not clear accessible actors cache when document becomes non-busy. r=pbro, a=RyanVM\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 9DwTcF3w4Eo", "files": ["devtools/server/actors/accessibility.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a375e2abdf85cee0cef056a4cfd108061db575a2", "parents": ["29db38642cdd088356987980748adce41cc40130"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tooru Fujisawa \u003carai_a@mac.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1454285 - Part 1: Specify the current scope when emitting await and .generator. r=jwalden, a=RyanVM", "files": ["js/src/frontend/BytecodeEmitter.cpp", "js/src/frontend/BytecodeEmitter.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9e0a6a5bbc1af21ccb6b467e6fbc6e95733d422c", "parents": ["a375e2abdf85cee0cef056a4cfd108061db575a2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tooru Fujisawa \u003carai_a@mac.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1454285 - Part 2: Disallow using innermostEmitterScope while the value does not match the bytecode environment. r=jwalden, a=RyanVM", "files": ["js/src/frontend/BytecodeEmitter.cpp", "js/src/frontend/BytecodeEmitter.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "be0e37593e171a8e832e49140deb0dd29d795bc5", "parents": ["9e0a6a5bbc1af21ccb6b467e6fbc6e95733d422c"], "tags": []}], "date": 1527093151, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "9253": {"changesets": [{"author": "menantea \u003cmenantea@linux.vnet.ibm.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1462566 - Add signal handling registers for powerpc. r=bbouvier, a=RyanVM", "files": ["js/src/wasm/WasmSignalHandlers.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "323494cc7e95da96e2189dc174477a66775e10b4", "parents": ["be0e37593e171a8e832e49140deb0dd29d795bc5"], "tags": []}], "date": 1527101043, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "9254": {"changesets": [{"author": "Gijs Kruitbosch \u003cgijskruitbosch@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1461407 - Make about:home unlinkable again and improve behavior of serialized principals across changes to URLs. r=bz,Mardak,mikedeboer, a=RyanVM\n\nMaking about:home unlinkable changes its URL structure. Prior to this change,\nit is a nested URL. After this change, it no longer is.\n\nWe store serialized versions of principals in some cases. These include\ndetails about whether the URI is nested etc. This is problematic for the\nabout:home change because the change in nesting changes the origin of the\npage, so the origin  would mismatch between the principal and its URL.\nTo avoid this, we always re-create URIs for about: URIs when deserializing\nthem from strings, ensuring we don't create bogus principals.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 87zVUFgbusn", "files": ["browser/components/about/AboutRedirector.cpp", "caps/ContentPrincipal.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7272335e193cb0500b4f3657245b4b0a1422899e", "parents": ["323494cc7e95da96e2189dc174477a66775e10b4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Alex Gaynor \u003cagaynor@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1456189 - Simplify BufferList::Extract to make the lifetimes clearer. r=froydnj, a=RyanVM", "files": ["mfbt/BufferList.h", "mfbt/tests/TestBufferList.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fbd069ce4e4dc5e2c724f1bc5b8d3ae7d34f0fa3", "parents": ["7272335e193cb0500b4f3657245b4b0a1422899e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Alex Gaynor \u003cagaynor@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1462912 - Fixed BufferList::Extract to handle the case where the call consumes the entirety of the BufferList. r=froydnj, a=RyanVM\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 1LWODn8JaNL", "files": ["mfbt/BufferList.h", "mfbt/tests/TestBufferList.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cef7f526b60ef27abc881356d12a10805ab730c9", "parents": ["fbd069ce4e4dc5e2c724f1bc5b8d3ae7d34f0fa3"], "tags": []}], "date": 1527106912, "git_changesets": [null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "9255": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump