 "desc": "Bug 1456485 - Part 2: Allow extensions with the mozillaAddons permission to match restricted schemes. r=zombie, a=RyanVM\n\nThe schema handling for this is currently a bit ugly, for the sake of\nsimplifying uplift. In the figure, we should find a way to change the schema\npattern matching based on whether or not the extension is privileged.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: CU9WR2Ika6k", "files": ["toolkit/components/extensions/Extension.jsm", "toolkit/components/extensions/ExtensionChild.jsm", "toolkit/components/extensions/WebExtensionContentScript.h", "toolkit/components/extensions/WebExtensionPolicy.cpp", "toolkit/components/extensions/extension-process-script.js", "toolkit/components/extensions/schemas/manifest.json", "toolkit/components/extensions/test/xpcshell/test_ext_contentscript_restrictSchemes.js", "toolkit/components/extensions/test/xpcshell/xpcshell-common.ini", "xpcom/ds/nsGkAtomList.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5c84b9f83fc65cc4ccfae88a8c1e566d7f27f823", "parents": ["e9ded0f757709b08a577689e62fbe82afed68042"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tim Nguyen \u003cntim.bugs@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1454232 - Use toolbarbutton-attention-fill for syncing animation. r=dao, a=RyanVM\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 87V68Vud2ep", "files": ["browser/themes/shared/customizableui/panelUI.inc.css", "browser/themes/shared/toolbarbutton-icons.inc.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e049dc25908cf34ecde90b6d47eb2aa1b896c132", "parents": ["5c84b9f83fc65cc4ccfae88a8c1e566d7f27f823"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tom Ritter \u003ctom@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1462891 - Add Timer Rounding to Navigation APIs. r=baku, a=RyanVM", "files": ["dom/performance/PerformanceNavigationTiming.cpp", "dom/performance/tests/mochitest.ini", "dom/performance/tests/test_performance_navigation_timing.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "30b75eae500bb1a8d6c21e0050ca606a9a7da0a6", "parents": [