03cgsquelart@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1464091 - Ignore case in media feature names inside media query expressions. r=heycam, a=RyanVM\n\nMedia feature names are converted to lower case before being processed, making\nthem effectively case-insensitive.\nPrefixes (\"min-\", etc.) and values are already treated in a case-insensitive\nmanner.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: JUeeEQEMIi4", "files": ["servo/components/style/gecko/media_queries.rs"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bbba8cee7041f692f3182a65687f272cc181f20d", "parents": ["70c46487e5132963906f5caab8e0181e7b5e772e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Gerald Squelart \u003cgsquelart@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1464091 - Test ascii-case-insensitivity of media query expressions. r=heycam, a=RyanVM\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 49pmJQXuvGo", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/MANIFEST.json", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/mediaqueries/mq-case-insensitive-001.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "91934961833a3e73e7f719d3dffda929422b6d00", "parents": ["bbba8cee7041f692f3182a65687f272cc181f20d"], "tags": []}], "date": 1528932777, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "9365": {"changesets": [{"author": "ffxbld", "branch": "default", "desc": "No Bug, mozilla-beta repo-update HSTS HPKP. r=RyanVM, a=release\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D1653", "files": ["security/manager/ssl/StaticHPKPins.h", "security/manager/ssl/nsSTSPreloadList.inc"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "585281dde9604ddd197693ca5330f2b95987a181", "parents": ["91934961833a3e73e7f719d3dffda929422b6d00"], "tags": ["DEVEDITION_61_0b14_BUILD1", "DEVEDITION_61_0b14_RELEASE", "FIREFOX_61_0b14_BUILD1", "FIREFOX_61_0b14_RELEASE"]}], "date": 1528984609, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "9366": {"changesets": [{"author": "\"Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e\"", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 585281dde9604ddd197693ca5330f2b95987a181 with DEVEDITION_61_0b14_BUILD1, DEVEDITION_61_0b14_RELEASE a=release CLOSED TREE", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "726241488be87daf73e9be9b8d3d7c933e7441e0", "parents": ["585281dde9604ddd197693ca5330f2b95987a181"], "tags": []}, {"author": "\"Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e\"", "branch": "default", "desc": "Automatic version bump CLOSED TREE NO BUG a=release", "files": ["browser/config/version_display.txt"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ce14576281c3a9023f70c3d80dd3a6e6b77272a0", "parents": ["726241488be87daf73e9be9b8d3d7c933e7441e0"], "tags": []}], "date": 1529073629, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "9367": {"changesets": [{"author": "\"Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e\"", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 585281dde9604ddd197693ca5330f2b95987a181 with FIREFOX_61_0b14_BUILD1, FIREFOX_61_0b14_RELEASE a=release CLOSED TREE", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ff652e865a9420ad2b42f84221df70ecb933f912", "parents": ["ce14576281c3a9023f70c3d80dd3a6e6b77272a0"], "tags": []}], "date": 1529073798, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "9368": {"changesets": [{"author": "Markus Stange \u003cmstange@themasta.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1462742 - Don't build display items for the custom content container frame twice during the same paint. r=emilio, a=RyanVM\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 6L2fygc1JCv", "files": ["layout/generic/ViewportFrame.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "39e52996f3328a386cd17f931b7101b36148a345", "parents": ["ff652e865a9420ad2b42f84221df70ecb933f912"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Shane Caraveo \u003cscaraveo@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1468830 - Ignore exceptions when retreiving response headers. r=rpl, a=RyanVM\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Dw4X1q15NHv", "files": ["toolkit/modules/addons/WebRequest.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "41e630d337759319125ba4cd44340c7e8d9fe6ef", "parents": ["39e52996f3328a386cd17f931b7101b36148a345"], "tags": []}], "date": 1529077287, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "9369": {"changesets": [{"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "THUNDERBIRD_60_VERBRANCH", "desc": "Bug 1423895: Don't use the XUL stylesheet cache if the parsing mode doesn't match. r=bz a=jorgk DONTBUILD\n\nEnigmail is loading a XUL document sheet that is @import-ed in another chrome://\nsheet.\n\nServo keys stuff off the origin of the sheet, which we derive from the parsing\nmode (see mode_to_origin in glue.rs).\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: LQqKmxToBKC", "files": ["layout/style/Loader.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fd5797b0b83a59ef4d2e69a342518eb5b5208173", "parents": ["475ee126be734dd153a18e93345026c843ab1634"], "tags": []}], "date": 1529226966, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "mozilla@jorgk.com"}, "9370": {"changesets": [{"author": "Paul Adenot \u003cpaul@paul.cx\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1461276 - Update telemetry probes for media. r=jya, datareview=chutten, a=RyanVM\n\nThis makes drno and jya the recipient for the media alert emails, removes\ncpearce, ajones, and also removes a few people that are not involved with the\nproject anymore (and the some emails were no longer valid anyways).\n\nAlso, bump a number of probes to 63, to get an updated picture of the data.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: EmlHyihnxIw", "files": ["toolkit/components/telemetry/Histograms.json", "toolkit/components/telemetry/histogram-whitelists.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0a3654c4831592d7b57010f33ee14d6b64ddfa27", "parents": ["41e630d337759319125ba4cd44340c7e8d9fe6ef"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Matt Woodrow \u003cmwoodrow@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1464928 - Invalidate border-collapse tables when we remove the border from a cell. r=mstange, a=RyanVM\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 4LWdFJkr72v", "files": ["layout/reftests/invalidation/reftest.list", "layout/reftests/invalidation/table-repaint-e-ref.html", "layout/reftests/invalidation/table-repaint-e.html", "layout/tables/nsTableCellFrame.cpp", "layout/tables/nsTableColFrame.cpp", "layout/tables/nsTableColGroupFrame.cpp", "layout/tables/nsTableRowFrame.cpp", "layout/tables/nsTableRowGroupFrame.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "53dfb0d88a603b8de7811b80013487103cef66bd", "parents": ["0a3654c4831592d7b57010f33ee14d6b64ddfa27"], "tags": []}, {"author": "David Keeler \u003cdkeeler@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1465562 - Ensure succeededCertChain is set in TLS handshakes with session resumption. r=fkiefer, a=RyanVM\n\nWhen doing TLS session resumption, Firefox currently does not have enough\ninformation to trivially reconstitute the original connection's security\ninformation. Consequently, we have to rebuild the certificate chain in the\nhandshake callback. Before this patch, we determined the EV and CT status of the\nconnection but did not set the succeeded cert chain unless the certificate was\nEV. This was insufficient. In this patch, we set the succeeded cert chain\nregardless of if the certificate is EV or not (provided we found a valid chain).\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: AuKrlBwX1Qh", "files": ["dom/cache/test/mochitest/mochitest.ini", "security/manager/ssl/nsNSSCallbacks.cpp", "security/manager/ssl/tests/unit/test_session_resumption.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e39e68b00278986028c5101f1cb612568e677096", "parents": ["53dfb0d88a603b8de7811b80013487103cef66bd"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nils Ohlmeier [:drno] \u003cdrno@ohlmeier.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1464063 - Remove sdp_getchoosetok. r=bwc, a=RyanVM", "files": ["media/webrtc/signaling/src/sdp/sipcc/sdp_private.h", "media/webrtc/signaling/src/sdp/sipcc/sdp_token.c", "media/webrtc/signaling/src/sdp/sipcc/sdp_utils.c"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3c164d94ac53fe3806bbebd173b74240da5fa5e8", "parents": ["e39e68b00278986028c5101f1cb612568e677096"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nicolas Silva \u003cnsilva@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1464039 - Reject some invalid transforms in qcms. r=mwoodrow, a=RyanVM", "files": ["gfx/qcms/chain.c"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1b1ae042aad242d0f2c29f6e7571e2f80e521188", "parents": ["3c164d94ac53fe3806bbebd173b74240da5fa5e8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "ffxbld", "branch": "default", "desc": "No Bug, mozilla-beta repo-update HSTS HPKP. r=RyanVM, a=release\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D1680", "files": ["security/manager/ssl/StaticHPKPins.h", "security/manager/ssl/nsSTSPreloadList.inc"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5ea5701969e649f5ac49da09983938dd5931d5a2", "parents": ["1b1ae042aad242d0f2c29f6e7571e2f80e521188"], "tags": ["FENNEC_61_0b15_BUILD1", "FENNEC_61_0b15_RELEASE"]}], "date": 1529330699, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "9371": {"changesets": [{"author": "ffxbld \u003crelease@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging mozilla-beta 5ea5701969e649f5ac49da09983938dd5931d5a2 with FIREFOX_RELEASE_61_BASE a=release DONTBUILD CLOSED TREE", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "45b7d45d04184c77c6b284e26c6fa500c75de36e", "parents": ["5ea5701969e649f5ac49da09983938dd5931d5a2"], "tags": []}], "date": 1529344479, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "mtabara@mozilla.com"}, "9372": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jordan Lund \u003cjlund@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Removed tag FIREFOX_RELEASE_61_BASE, DONTBUILD CLOSED TREE r=backout, a=npotb", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents